results.description:
This photo has beauty within, the two classical elements: water and stone. Nevertheless it also indicates the two major issues to worry in Finland. The Baltic Sea is one of the most shallow and most polluted seas of the world. There is a major problem of eutrophication, lack of oxygen and warming waters (global warming). This has led to am really nasty toxic algae problem in the Baltic sea. 

Stone reminds me of the other major issue in Finland: Mining. Finland has one of the most company friendly laws in mining. This has led to a mining boost in Finland, which endangers large natural areas.
